fc: class Solution { public:     ListNode *getIntersectionNode(ListNode *headA, ListNode *headB) {         ListNode *a = headA, *b = headB;         while (a != b) {             a = a ? a->next : headB;             b = b ? b->next : headA;         }         return a;     } };

fm: vector<int> twoSum(vector<int> &numbers, int target) {         vector<int> ret;         int i = 0, j = numbers.size() - 1;         while (i < j) {             if (numbers[i] + numbers[j] == target)                 break;             else if (numbers[i] + numbers[j] > target)                 --j;             else                 ++i;         }         ret.push_back(i + 1);         ret.push_back(j + 1);         return ret;     }

fm: int majorityElement(vector<int> &nums) {         int maj = 0, max_n = 0;         unordered_map<int, int> m;         for (auto n : nums) {             if (m.find(n) == m.end())                 m[n] = 0;             ++m[n];             if (max_n < m[n]) {                 max_n = m[n];                 maj = n;             }         }         return maj;     }
fc: class Solution { public:     int majorityElement(vector<int> &nums) {         int maj = 0, max_n = 0;         unordered_map<int, int> m;         for (auto n : nums) {             if (m.find(n) == m.end())                 m[n] = 0;             ++m[n];             if (max_n < m[n]) {                 max_n = m[n];                 maj = n;             }         }         return maj;     } };
